\hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 n\hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 \hich\f1  shall be referred to as a \'93\loch\f1 \hich\f1 Mini Harsh Environment UPS\'94\loch\f1  or Mini-HEUPS System, Model LU0.4, LU0.7, LU1.5, and LU1.6.  
