\ltrch\fcs0 \fs20\insrsid7748226 \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 While the Mini-HEUPS has sophisticated cooling technology to prevent over heating, in the event of an over temperature conditi\hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 
on the Mini-HEUPS will shut down.  The Mini-HEUPS has an auto recovery feature, which turns the unit "On" when temperatures have cooled sufficiently. The Mini-HEUPS has built-in hysteresis feature to prevent oscillation at the cut off temperature of 85C. 

