The UPS shall be protected from surges resulting from lightning strikes.  AC and DC connections fed by utility shall be protected.  The User Alarm interface shall also be protected from such surges to the same specifications as telecommunication protector
\hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1  \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 block usage. 
\par }\pard\plain \ltrpar\qc \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 \rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs24\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1042\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af31505\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1042 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs20 \ltrch\fcs0 
